> Page2

All white. A sound of running footsteps becomes clearer...

> Page3

                                                                                You are a man, running down a blind alley.

> Page4

                                                                                Someone is chasing you. Two guys wearing balaclavas.

> Page5

                                                                                You run faster, trying to leave them behind. But they seem to be getting closer to you.

> Page6

                                                                                Stumbles. You try throwing them obstacles: a basket supermarket, an empty barrel, a waste container. Doesn't matter, they continue behind you. Just a littler more and-

> Page7

                                                                                PAM! With a kick you open the emergency door of an old apartment building, and begins to climb the stairs.

> Page8

                                                                                You reach the first floor, and they kick the door. UP

> Page9

                                                                                Second floor and the masked say something, but you can not stop to hear them. DOWN

> Page10

                                                                                They insult you. One is left behind. UP

> Page11

                                                                                Third floor and you trip and fall a few steps. DOWN

> Page12

                                                                                One of them takes you from one leg, but you kicks him in the face and make him fall on the other man.. And UP

> Page13

                                                                                In the fourth floor you continue down a hallway to a room.

> Page14

                                                                                You go inside and lock the door with the key and the door latches.

> Page15

                                                                                You evaluate your chances, while the noises are coming..
The apartment is very messy-all the stuff lying around. The guys knock on the door.

> Page16

                                                                                —Open the fucking door! Now!

                                                                                Now you are free to choice, but still feel the pressure on your shoulders, the limits of the duty calling you to do something and fast.  You need to take reasonable decisions, to not waste time. Strangers come inside from one moment to another... Not many options, but you have to decide quickly

approach the TV

go to the balcony

search the drawers and the closet

> Page17

                                                                                You turn on the device. The two men hit the door again, this time with more enthusiasm. On the screen a news channel is announcing the weather. The woman who presented the section is wearing a balaclava too. You moves away, scared. Strangers stop banging on the door for a moment.

Walk to the balcony

Search the drawers and the closet

> Page19

                                                                                to approach the abyss and look down. Dizziness taking you by surprise when you see that every person on the street are wearing balaclavas.
The guys begin to break the lock with a kind of bar.

Finally, you search the drawers and the closet

> Page20

                                                                                looking for something important. PAM!

> Page37

                                                                                You pull all the clothes on the floor. Check old shoeboxes. But there's nothing of what you want.

> Page21

                                                                                You got it. It is an old suitcase. You open it. PAM, PAM... PAM!

> Page22

                                                                                You found it. A balaclava. You put yourself quickly, just as the two strangers thrown down the door and enter the apartment. They point you with guns.

> Page23

                                                                                You are on your knees on the floor. You turns around and tells them.:
—Not me, you are wrong.

> Page24

